item.title: CVE-2022-34772|2024-09-17T02:57:43.020Z -- tabit -- tabit
item.description: Tabit - password enumeration. Description: Tabit - password enumeration. The passwords for the Tabit system is a 4 digit OTP. One can resend OTP and try logging in indefinitely. Once again, this is an example of OWASP: API4 - Rate limiting.
